Class Rental

    • Rental

      public Rental(int tenant_id, int user_id, int room_id, LocalDate check_in_date, LocalDate check_out_date, double total_amount)
      Creates a new Rental object with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      tenant_id - The ID of the tenant renting the room.
      user_id - The ID of the user managing the rental.
      room_id - The ID of the room being rented.
      check_in_date - The date the tenant will move in.
      check_out_date - The date the tenant will move out.
      total_amount - The total amount due for the rental period.
